25|$|Although {{peace is}} widely {{perceived}} as something intangible, various {{organizations have been}} making efforts to quantify and measure it. The Global <b>Peace</b> <b>Index</b> produced by the Institute <b>for</b> Economics and <b>Peace</b> is a known effort to evaluate peacefulness in countries based on 23 indicators of the presence/absence of violence.|$|R
